The antioxidant activity of MpEO was compared to that
of silymarin, a well-known antioxidant, using two different
assays, namely DPPH and superoxide oxygen radicals in-
hibition, the results are reported in Table 2. DPPH showed
for MpEO an IC50 value around 3 times higher than the
one recorded for silymarin indicating that antioxidant
activity of MpEO was lower than that of silymarin.
